text: Alblasserdam is a municipality and town in the province of South Holland, the Netherlands. About 20,000 people were living there in 2021. It lies on the east bank of the Noord river in the Alblasserwaard region. == References == * Plaatsengids.nl Category:Municipalities of South Holland Category:Settlements in South Holland Category:Alblasserwaard
